com.amazonaws.services.dynamodbv2.datamodeling.encryption

Class EncryptionContext.Builder

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.amazonaws.services.dynamodbv2.datamodeling.encryption.EncryptionContext.Builder
  • Enclosing class:
    EncryptionContext

    public static final class EncryptionContext.Builder
extends Object
    Builder class for EncryptionContext. Mutable objects (other than developerContext) will undergo a defensive copy prior to being stored in the builder. This class is not thread-safe.
